RDS Instance
•	Create a RDS MySQL instance
o	Use Free Tier
o	Username will be 'admin' and you can set password (you can't use
special character)
o	Keep the Public access to True to access it from Local or remote server
o	Create a security group (and allow 3306 from everywhere)
o	After creating, you can find Endpoint (hostname) to connect to this DB



EC2 Instance
